        {
            "title": "英國2月經濟增長超出預期",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/miXohvcB3fZEOhf9OghfXw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/world_news_2_108x81.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 根據國家統計局週四發布的官方數據,英國經濟在2月份實現增長,超出分析師預期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">月度數據超過了路透社調查經濟學家預測的0.1%增幅。該數據緊隨1月份上修後的0.1%增長之後。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此次增長由廣泛板塊的強勁表現推動,服務業活動環比上升0.5%,工業生產環比增長0.5%。儘管2月份天氣異常潮濕,建築業產出仍環比大幅增長1.0%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">多個能源密集型板塊在2月份錄得強勁增長。採礦和採石業產出環比上升3.9%,批發和零售業增長0.7%,運輸和倉儲業增長0.4%,藝術、娛樂和休閒業大幅增長2.0%。住宿和餐飲業產出環比下降0.3%,製造業產出環比下降0.1%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-0a047923-5e9c-38a6-83e6-af0951dba79f-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">2月份的強勁表現可能將第一季度GDP增長推升至約0.6%的季度環比增幅,高於Capital Economics此前預估的0.3%季度環比增幅。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Capital Economics預計,由於伊朗戰爭導致能源價格上漲的影響,GDP增長將從2025年的1.4%放緩至2026年的約0.7%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">3月份的活動採購經理人指數顯示,增長已經大幅放緩。在不利情境下,2026年GDP增長可能僅為0.3%。這些預測與戰前預測的1.0%形成對比。</p></div>",
